{"tid":2057878,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無故取消外賣 至少囚6年","createTime":"2020-06-09T17:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T18:10:32.000Z","uid":5995,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3ca2c7f395caf46b9f9dbd39154c678b0cc575","tid":2057878,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"菲律賓眾議員加爾班（Alfredo Garbin）日前提交一項法案，訂立條例針對惡意取消外賣訂單的人，違者將被判處至少6年監禁並罰款10萬菲律賓披索（約港幣1.55萬元）。加爾班表示，最主要目的是希望民眾尊重外賣服務，同時保障外賣員及商店權益，條例目前仍有很多調整空間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">法案亦有訂明，若顧客在任何平台上對外賣員有羞辱等不當言詞，亦會將被判處至少6個月的監禁</span>。但如果是外賣員延誤送達時間1小時以上，或顧客使用信用卡取消訂單不退款，這類情況則可合理取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1791687/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E7%84%A1%E6%95%85%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%9B%9A6%E5%B9%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1791687%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25B3%2593%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%259B%259A6%25E5%25B9%25B4&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelgXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=065bdfa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1791687%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25B3%2593%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%259B%259A6%25E5%25B9%25B4&h=edbf860a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1791687/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9